et Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider. Pruritus therapeutics market to reach $15.58 Bn by 2035, driven by rising skin disorders, strong biologics pipeline, and expanding global treatment demand. Austin, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- According to SNS Insider,", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263619/0/en/Pruritus-Therapeutics-Market-Size-is-Projected-to-Reach-USD-15-58-Billion-by-2035-Due-to-the-Increasing-Cases-of-Chronic-Inflammatory-Skin-Diseases-Globally-SNS-Insider.html", "title": "Pruritus Therapeutics Market Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:00Z"}}, "41": {"text": "(GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- According to SNS Insider, the\u00a0Pruritus Therapeutics Market\u00a0size was valued at USD 10.30 billion in 2025 and is expected to reach USD 15.58 billion by 2035, \u2026 [+8984 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263619/0/en/Pruritus-Therapeutics-Market-Size-is-Projected-to-Reach-USD-15-58-Billion-by-2035-Due-to-the-Increasing-Cases-of-Chronic-Inflammatory-Skin-Diseases-Globally-SNS-Insider.html", "title": "Pruritus Therapeutics Market Size is Projected to Reach USD 15.58 Billion by 2035 Due to the Increasing Cases of Chronic Inflammatory Skin Diseases Globally | SNS Insider", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T09:30:00Z"}}, "42": {"text": "5 kitchen splurges that I can't recommend enough. The right kitchen tools really can make your life easier. These are some of my favorite upgrade picks, all discounted during Amazon's Big Spring Sale. ZDNET's recommendations are based on many hours of testing, research, and comparison shopping. We gather data from the best available sources, including vendor and retailer listings as well as other", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.zdnet.com/home-and-office/kitchen-household/kitchen-splurges-amazon-spring-sale-2026/", "title": "5 kitchen splurges that I can't recommend enough", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:51Z"}}, "43": {"text": "vendor and retailer listings as well as other \u2026 [+1153 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.zdnet.com/home-and-office/kitchen-household/kitchen-splurges-amazon-spring-sale-2026/", "title": "5 kitchen splurges that I can't recommend enough", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:51Z"}}, "44": {"text": "All the iPhone Lock Screen Changes You Might Have Missed in iOS 26. The update brought more to your device's lock screen than just the big clock. Apple released\u00a0iOS 26\u00a0in\u00a0September, and in addition to new features like\u00a0call screening, the update also brought more customization options to your iPhone's lock screen.\r\nWhen the tech giant released\u2026 [+4058 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.cnet.com/tech/services-and-software/apple-iphone-ios-26-lock-screen/", "title": "All the iPhone Lock Screen Changes You Might Have Missed in iOS 26", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:51Z"}}, "45": {"text": "6 E-Bikes That Define Where Electric Riding Is Headed in 2026. The electric bike market isn\u2019t just growing anymore. It\u2019s splitting into distinct lanes, each one moving fast enough to make last year\u2019s picks feel dated. Commuters want torque sensors and integrated smart systems. Adventure riders want fat tires and full sus\u2026 If you buy something from a link in this article, we may earn a commission.", "metadata": {"source": "https://the-gadgeteer.com/2026/03/27/6-e-bikes-that-define-where-electric-riding-is-headed-in-2026/", "title": "6 E-Bikes That Define Where Electric Riding Is Headed in 2026", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:39Z"}}, "46": {"text": "a link in this article, we may earn a commission. Learn more", "metadata": {"source": "https://the-gadgeteer.com/2026/03/27/6-e-bikes-that-define-where-electric-riding-is-headed-in-2026/", "title": "6 E-Bikes That Define Where Electric Riding Is Headed in 2026", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:39Z"}}, "47": {"text": "The electric bike market isnt just growing anymore. Its splitting into distinct lanes, each one moving fast eno\u2026 [+9065 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://the-gadgeteer.com/2026/03/27/6-e-bikes-that-define-where-electric-riding-is-headed-in-2026/", "title": "6 E-Bikes That Define Where Electric Riding Is Headed in 2026", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:39Z"}}, "48": {"text": "Dad won\u2019t talk about estate planning. How can I avoid being blindsided?. FP Answers: Think about what will motivate him to convey a plan, such as peace of mind, income tax or an aversion to involving lawyers Q. I am an only child but my dad is very quiet on estate planning. I am unsure what to do at this point. Im 40 years old and my dad is 67 years old. He owns a home, a boat, three cars and a", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/fp-answers/dad-wont-talk-estate-planning-avoid-blindsided", "title": "Dad won\u2019t talk about estate planning. How can I avoid being blindsided?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:34Z"}}, "49": {"text": "old. He owns a home, a boat, three cars and a cat. He i\u2026 [+6029 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/fp-answers/dad-wont-talk-estate-planning-avoid-blindsided", "title": "Dad won\u2019t talk about estate planning. How can I avoid being blindsided?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:34Z"}}, "50": {"text": "Jack Mintz: Energy security will top many nations\u2019 future political agendas. If the Strait of Hormuz is no longer safe,\u00a0Saudi Arabia and Gulf States\u00a0will\u00a0need\u00a0other\u00a0ways to deliver\u00a0oil to the global market. Read more. With the closing of the Strait of Hormuz to non-Iranian shipments of oil, the world is keeping close watch on oil prices. Energy security is now paramount, not ESG or climate change.", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/opinion/energy-security-top-nations-future-political-agendas", "title": "Jack Mintz: Energy security will top many nations\u2019 future political agendas", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:18Z"}}, "51": {"text": "is now paramount, not ESG or climate change. Higher gas and d\u2026 [+5010 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/opinion/energy-security-top-nations-future-political-agendas", "title": "Jack Mintz: Energy security will top many nations\u2019 future political agendas", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:18Z"}}, "52": {"text": "Don Jr.\u2019s shadow hangs over Trump mine fight as China retains critical minerals leverage. Trump's push for domestic mining faces contradiction as his administration defends Biden's EPA veto blocking Alaska's copper-rich Pebble mine project. President Donald Trumps push to expand U.S. mining and loosen Chinas global grip on critical minerals is colliding with his administrations defense in court of", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.foxnews.com/politics/don-jr-s-shadow-hangs-over-trump-mine-fight-china-retains-critical-minerals-leverage", "title": "Don Jr.\u2019s shadow hangs over Trump mine fight as China retains critical minerals leverage", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:13Z"}}, "53": {"text": "with his administrations defense in court of a Biden-era veto blocking Alaskas coppe\u2026 [+7676 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.foxnews.com/politics/don-jr-s-shadow-hangs-over-trump-mine-fight-china-retains-critical-minerals-leverage", "title": "Don Jr.\u2019s shadow hangs over Trump mine fight as China retains critical minerals leverage", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:13Z"}}, "54": {"text": "Why Is Pam Bondi Ducking Epstein Questions?. She claims to run a historically transparent Justice Department. So why does she seem eager to avoid testifying to Congress again?, wonders legal columnist Elie Honig. This is the most transparent Justice Department in the history of the United States and maybe all of human existence. Just ask them.", "metadata": {"source": "http://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/why-is-pam-bondi-ducking-epstein-questions.html", "title": "Why Is Pam Bondi Ducking Epstein Questions?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:01Z"}}, "55": {"text": "When pressed in November 2025 about DOJs handling of the Epstein \u2026 [+7997 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "http://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/why-is-pam-bondi-ducking-epstein-questions.html", "title": "Why Is Pam Bondi Ducking Epstein Questions?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:01Z"}}, "56": {"text": "UFL rosters 2026: The former NFL, college names you'll recognize in football league. The UFL has some former NFL and college football players you'll recognize in 2026. UFL rosters 2026: The former NFL, college names you'll recognize in football league originally appeared on The Sporting News. Add The Sporting News as a Preferred Source by clicking here.\r\nSpring foo\u2026 [+7321 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.sportingnews.com/us/nfl/news/ufl-rosters-2026-nfl-college-names/d3ce6ea62498871650271092", "title": "UFL rosters 2026: The former NFL, college names you'll recognize in football league", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:01Z"}}, "57": {"text": "The Bicycle and the New Woman. by Kimberly Keagan When you think of a bicycle, you probably picture a leisurely ride through the park or a way to get exercise. (Or somethi... by Kimberly KeaganWhen you think of a bicycle, you probably picture a leisurely ride through the park or a way to get exercise. (Or something you have to watch out for when you're driving!) But in th\u2026 [+3013 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.hhhistory.com/2026/03/the-bicycle-craze-of-late-19th-century.html", "title": "The Bicycle and the New Woman", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "58": {"text": "Friday Roundtable: First Transit Trip. When did you start riding public transit independently? Were there certain pivotal trips that made you more of a transit enthusiast and shaped your viewpoint? What\u2019s the youngest people you see now taking transit independently? The full 2 Line opens tomorrow,\u2026 When did you start riding public transit independently? Were there certain pivotal trips that made", "metadata": {"source": "https://seattletransitblog.com/2026/03/27/friday-roundtable-first-transit-trip/", "title": "Friday Roundtable: First Transit Trip", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "59": {"text": "Were there certain pivotal trips that made you more of a transit enthusiast and shaped your viewpoint? What\u2019s the youngest people you see now t\u2026 [+6501 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://seattletransitblog.com/2026/03/27/friday-roundtable-first-transit-trip/", "title": "Friday Roundtable: First Transit Trip", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "60": {"text": "Li Auto Inc. Announces Put Right Notification for 0.25% Convertible Senior Notes due 2028. BEIJING, China, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Li Auto Inc. (\u201cLi Auto\u201d or the \u201cCompany\u201d) (Nasdaq: LI; HKEX: 2015), a leader in China\u2019s new energy vehicle market, today announced that it is notifying holders of its 0.25% Convertible Senior Notes due 2028 (\u2026 BEIJING, China, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE)", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263632/0/en/Li-Auto-Inc-Announces-Put-Right-Notification-for-0-25-Convertible-Senior-Notes-due-2028.html", "title": "Li Auto Inc. Announces Put Right Notification for 0.25% Convertible Senior Notes due 2028", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "61": {"text": "BEIJING, China, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Li Auto Inc. (Li Auto or the Company) (Nasdaq: LI; HKEX: 2015), a leader in Chinas new energy vehicle market, today announced that it is notifying h\u2026 [+6119 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263632/0/en/Li-Auto-Inc-Announces-Put-Right-Notification-for-0-25-Convertible-Senior-Notes-due-2028.html", "title": "Li Auto Inc. Announces Put Right Notification for 0.25% Convertible Senior Notes due 2028", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "62": {"text": "Germany news: Bundestag votes for pension scheme reboot. German lawmakers have voted for a scheme aimed at making state-backed private pensions more attractive. Meanwhile, the center-left Social Democrats are taking stock of their latest electoral defeats. DW has the latest. Germany's parliament has voted to replace the underperforming \"Riester\" pension system with a new state-backed savings", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dw.com/en/germany-news-bundestag-votes-for-pension-scheme-reboot/live-76558121", "title": "Germany news: Bundestag votes for pension scheme reboot", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "63": {"text": "pension system with a new state-backed savings model.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dw.com/en/germany-news-bundestag-votes-for-pension-scheme-reboot/live-76558121", "title": "Germany news: Bundestag votes for pension scheme reboot", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "64": {"text": "The current system, introduced in 2002, has proven\u00a0unpopular because it \u2026 [+1260 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.dw.com/en/germany-news-bundestag-votes-for-pension-scheme-reboot/live-76558121", "title": "Germany news: Bundestag votes for pension scheme reboot", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "65": {"text": "Southwest customers slam airline\u2019s \u2018fat tax\u2019 policy \u2014 after \u2018embarrassed\u2019 traveler slapped with $1,000 second seat. Furious customers are sounding off about the new policy. Talk about some sky-high baggage fees.\r\nFurious Southwest Airlines customers are sounding off over the carriers controversial new policy which critics have slammed as a so-called fat tax after one tr\u2026 [+3825 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://nypost.com/2026/03/27/lifestyle/southwest-airlines-new-fat-tax-policy/", "title": "Southwest customers slam airline\u2019s \u2018fat tax\u2019 policy \u2014 after \u2018embarrassed\u2019 traveler slapped with $1,000 second seat", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "66": {"text": "What next for Craig Bellamy and his exciting brand of football?. It wasn't supposed to end that way. Wales were certainly confident they would progress to Tuesday's World Cup play-off final and most were predicting it would be a showdown against Italy. It wasn't supposed to end that way. Wales were certainly confident they would progress to Tuesday's World Cup play-off final and most were", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/13524903/wales-reporter-notebook-world-cup-dreams-are-over-but-what-next-for-craig-bellamy-and-his-exciting-brand-of-football", "title": "What next for Craig Bellamy and his exciting brand of football?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "67": {"text": "Tuesday's World Cup play-off final and most were predicting it would be a showdown against Italy.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/13524903/wales-reporter-notebook-world-cup-dreams-are-over-but-what-next-for-craig-bellamy-and-his-exciting-brand-of-football", "title": "What next for Craig Bellamy and his exciting brand of football?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "68": {"text": "Despite It\u2026 [+4834 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/13524903/wales-reporter-notebook-world-cup-dreams-are-over-but-what-next-for-craig-bellamy-and-his-exciting-brand-of-football", "title": "What next for Craig Bellamy and his exciting brand of football?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z"}}, "69": {"text": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister. Balendra Shah was sworn in a day after he released his first public statement since winning the Mar 5 elections, via a rap song posted on social media. KATHMANDU: Nepal's rapper-turned-politician Balendra Shah was sworn in as prime minister on Friday (Mar 27) after sweeping the first election since deadly anti-corruption protests toppled the governm\u2026", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.channelnewsasia.com/asia/nepal-rapper-balendra-shah-sworn-in-prime-minister-6021191", "title": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:00Z"}}, "70": {"text": "anti-corruption protests toppled the governm\u2026 [+2339 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.channelnewsasia.com/asia/nepal-rapper-balendra-shah-sworn-in-prime-minister-6021191", "title": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:00Z"}}, "71": {"text": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show. Russia\u2019s crucial Baltic oil ports of Primorsk and Ust-Luga are on fire again after overnight drone attacks, according to data from NASA. (Bloomberg) Russias crucial Baltic oil ports of Primorsk and Ust-Luga are on fire again after overnight drone attacks, according to data from NASA.\r\nTHIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/russias-key-baltic-oil-ports-on-fire-again-satellite-data-show", "title": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:07:06Z"}}, "72": {"text": "THIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY\r\nSub\u2026 [+4120 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/russias-key-baltic-oil-ports-on-fire-again-satellite-data-show", "title": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:07:06Z"}}, "73": {"text": "Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai. Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai ~Sky City Mall, Borivali welcomes the brands second store in India~\r\nMUMBAI, India,\u00a0March 26, 2026\u00a0/PRNewswire/ -- OVS, Italys leading fashion retailer, has officially opened its first store in Mumba\u2026 [+4312 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/brandhub/pr-release/italian-fashion-leader-ovs-opens-its-first-store-in-mumbai/article70791895.ece", "title": "Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:25Z"}}, "74": {"text": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size. Cityflo is expanding its bus services to Kolkata and boosting its fleet in Delhi-NCR. The company now operates over 1,000 buses, three times its size last year. This move makes Cityflo a leading app-based bus operator in India. It aims to provide reliable, pr\u2026 Mumbai: Cityflo said it has scaled its operations in Delhi-NCR and entered Kolkata,", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/roadways/cityflo-enters-new-cities-triples-its-fleet-size/articleshow/129844248.cms", "title": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:03Z"}}, "75": {"text": "its operations in Delhi-NCR and entered Kolkata, taking its total fleet to more than 1,000 buses, three times last years size. The move positions the company among \u2026 [+1775 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/roadways/cityflo-enters-new-cities-triples-its-fleet-size/articleshow/129844248.cms", "title": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:03Z"}}, "76": {"text": "Indonesia\u2019s P2P Lending Grows 25%, JULO Strengthens Credit Quality. Indonesia's P2P Lending Grows 25%, JULO Strengthens Credit Quality JAKARTA, Indonesia,\u00a0March 26, 2026\u00a0/PRNewswire/ -- Indonesias\u00a0fintech lending (P2P lending) industry continues to demonstrate strong growth. Data from the Financial Services Authority (OJK) shows tha\u2026 [+4899 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/brandhub/pr-release/indonesias-p2p-lending-grows-25-julo-strengthens-credit-quality/article70791486.ece", "title": "Indonesia\u2019s P2P Lending Grows 25%, JULO Strengthens Credit Quality", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:05:36Z"}}, "77": {"text": "Hong Kong\u2019s Largest Standalone Intelligent Computing Hub \u2014 The Official Launch of China Mobile Global Intelligence Center. Hong Kong's Largest Standalone Intelligent Computing Hub \u2014 The Official Launch of China Mobile Global Intelligence Center HONG KONG,\u00a0March 26, 2026\u00a0/PRNewswire/ --\u00a0China Mobile held the opening ceremony for its Global Intelligence Center today in Hong Kong, under the theme", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/brandhub/pr-release/hong-kongs-largest-standalone-intelligent-computing-hub-the-official-launch-of-china-mobile-global-intelligence-center/article70791539.ece", "title": "Hong Kong\u2019s Largest Standalone Intelligent Computing Hub \u2014 The Official Launch of China Mobile Global Intelligence Center", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:05:35Z"}}, "78": {"text": "Center today in Hong Kong, under the theme Intelligence Connects All, Computing Ignites a \u2026 [+8663 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/brandhub/pr-release/hong-kongs-largest-standalone-intelligent-computing-hub-the-official-launch-of-china-mobile-global-intelligence-center/article70791539.ece", "title": "Hong Kong\u2019s Largest Standalone Intelligent Computing Hub \u2014 The Official Launch of China Mobile Global Intelligence Center", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:05:35Z"}}, "79": {"text": "Cowboys Headlines: Lots to love at Texas Tech pro day; Myles Garrett trade back in play?. From David Bailey to Jacob Rodriguez and Romello Height, there was lots to love in Lubbock. And could Myles Garrett be back on the trade block? Defense continues to be the watchword in Dallas as Cowboys coaches and scouts have fanned out to pro days across the country this week, looking to identify who they", "metadata": {"source": "https://cowboyswire.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/cowboys/2026/03/27/news-headlines-march-26-2026-texas-tech-pro-day-myles-garrett-trade/89342343007/", "title": "Cowboys Headlines: Lots to love at Texas Tech pro day; Myles Garrett trade back in play?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:05:28Z"}}, "80": {"text": "country this week, looking to identify who they might target with their draft pick\u2026 [+4207 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://cowboyswire.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/cowboys/2026/03/27/news-headlines-march-26-2026-texas-tech-pro-day-myles-garrett-trade/89342343007/", "title": "Cowboys Headlines: Lots to love at Texas Tech pro day; Myles Garrett trade back in play?", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:05:28Z"}}, "81": {"text": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Offers Disney Lorcana Discounts On Booster Boxes, Gift Bundles, and More. Save on Lorcana starter sets and Disney booster boxes in Amazon's latest Spring Sale deals. Disney Lorcana", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.ign.com/articles/amazons-spring-sale-offers-disney-lorcana-discounts-on-booster-boxes-gift-bundles-and-more", "title": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Offers Disney Lorcana Discounts On Booster Boxes, Gift Bundles, and More", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:58Z"}}, "82": {"text": "hits that sweet spot of offering a cavalcade of classic characters to collect, as well as being a fun and surprisingly deep TCG, and thanks to Amazons Spring Sale, you can save a fai\u2026 [+1913 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.ign.com/articles/amazons-spring-sale-offers-disney-lorcana-discounts-on-booster-boxes-gift-bundles-and-more", "title": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Offers Disney Lorcana Discounts On Booster Boxes, Gift Bundles, and More", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:58Z"}}, "83": {"text": "What channel is Tennessee baseball vs Vanderbilt on today? Time, TV schedule to watch game. What channel is the Tennessee baseball vs Vanderbilt game on today? Here's how to watch, including time, TV schedule, live streaming info and game odds. Tennessee baseball travels west for a three-game series against Vanderbilt, beginning on March 27 in Nashville.Vanderbilt (14-12, 2-4) was swept at", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.knoxnews.com/story/sports/college/university-of-tennessee/other-sports/2026/03/27/tennessee-baseball-vanderbilt-channel-today-time-tv-schedule-streaming-info/89323908007/", "title": "What channel is Tennessee baseball vs Vanderbilt on today? Time, TV schedule to watch game", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:45Z"}}, "84": {"text": "in Nashville.Vanderbilt (14-12, 2-4) was swept at Mississippi State last weekend amid a challenging s\u2026 [+1868 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.knoxnews.com/story/sports/college/university-of-tennessee/other-sports/2026/03/27/tennessee-baseball-vanderbilt-channel-today-time-tv-schedule-streaming-info/89323908007/", "title": "What channel is Tennessee baseball vs Vanderbilt on today? Time, TV schedule to watch game", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:45Z"}}, "85": {"text": "Just Eat under UK probe over 'misleading' reviews. Food delivery giant Just Eat is among five firms under investigation by the UK's competition watchdog as part of its crackdown on fake and misleading online reviews. Food delivery giant Just Eat is among five firms under investigation by the UK's competition watchdog as part of its crackdown on fake and misleading online reviews.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.rte.ie/news/business/2026/0327/1565479-uk-fake-reviews/", "title": "Just Eat under UK probe over 'misleading' reviews", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:03Z"}}, "86": {"text": "The Competition and Markets Auth\u2026 [+2731 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.rte.ie/news/business/2026/0327/1565479-uk-fake-reviews/", "title": "Just Eat under UK probe over 'misleading' reviews", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:03Z"}}, "87": {"text": "Axi Launches New Axi Select Webinar Series Following Successful Bloomberg Campaign. SYDNEY, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) \u2014 Global online trading provider Axi has announced the launch of a new educational webinar series under its Axi Select programme, expanding its trader education initiative following the successful completion of its rece\u2026 SYDNEY, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) Global online", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/globe-newswire/axi-launches-new-axi-select-webinar-series-following-successful-bloomberg-campaign", "title": "Axi Launches New Axi Select Webinar Series Following Successful Bloomberg Campaign", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:02Z"}}, "88": {"text": "March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) Global online trading provider Axi has announced the launch of a new educational webinar series under its Axi Select programme, expanding its trader education \u2026 [+4791 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/globe-newswire/axi-launches-new-axi-select-webinar-series-following-successful-bloomberg-campaign", "title": "Axi Launches New Axi Select Webinar Series Following Successful Bloomberg Campaign", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:04:02Z"}}, "89": {"text": "2026 NFL Draft landing spots for Alabama QB Ty Simpson. Ty Simpson's name will be called in the 2026 NFL Draft, but the team that will make the call remains a mystery. Here's some of the top landing spots. Fit is everything.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/draft/2026/03/27/ty-simpson-landing-spots-nfl-draft-jets-browns/89308724007/", "title": "2026 NFL Draft landing spots for Alabama QB Ty Simpson", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:03:39Z"}}, "90": {"text": "When it comes to the NFL draft, teams are hoping to find the right fit for each prospect. And when it comes to quarterbacks, nothing is more important than getting the right fit.\r\u2026 [+7041 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/nfl/draft/2026/03/27/ty-simpson-landing-spots-nfl-draft-jets-browns/89308724007/", "title": "2026 NFL Draft landing spots for Alabama QB Ty Simpson", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:03:39Z"}}, "91": {"text": "The Nothing Phone 4a Pro is doing better than even Nothing expected. Nothing launched the Nothing Phone 4a series earlier this month, and it seems like the company might have a sales hit on its hands. <ul><li>Nothing co-founder Carl Pei claimed that the Nothing Phone 4a Pro is selling way over target.</li><li>Pei didnt reveal more details about the actual target, so its possible the firm had a", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.androidauthority.com/nothing-phone-4a-pro-sales-over-target-3652530/", "title": "The Nothing Phone 4a Pro is doing better than even Nothing expected", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:03:26Z"}}, "92": {"text": "the actual target, so its possible the firm had a mod\u2026 [+1584 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.androidauthority.com/nothing-phone-4a-pro-sales-over-target-3652530/", "title": "The Nothing Phone 4a Pro is doing better than even Nothing expected", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:03:26Z"}}, "93": {"text": "Making Their Case: 7 Saudis out to impress in World Cup warm-up. Nothing is set in stone.That is the message from Herve Renard after naming an extended 50-man squad for this international window, split into \u201cA\u201d and \u201cB\u201d camps as he casts a wide net ahead of ... Nothing is set in stone.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.spl.com.sa/en/news/1013940/making-their-case-7-saudis-out-to-impress-in-world-cup-warm-up", "title": "Making Their Case: 7 Saudis out to impress in World Cup warm-up", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:15:00Z"}}, "94": {"text": "That is the message from Herve Renard after naming an extended 50-man squad for this international window, split into A and B camps as he casts a wide net ahead of this summ\u2026 [+4140 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.spl.com.sa/en/news/1013940/making-their-case-7-saudis-out-to-impress-in-world-cup-warm-up", "title": "Making Their Case: 7 Saudis out to impress in World Cup warm-up", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:15:00Z"}}, "95": {"text": "A nonprofit in France is fighting fast-fashion waste, one sneaker at a time. Hundreds of used sneakers arrive each week at a workshop east of Paris, where workers inspect them for resale, redistribution or rejection PARIS -- Hundreds of used sneakers arrive each week at a workshop east of Paris, where workers inspect them and ask a simple question: Can a shoe be saved?", "metadata": {"source": "https://abcnews.com/Business/wireStory/nonprofit-france-fighting-fast-fashion-waste-sneaker-time-131461818", "title": "A nonprofit in France is fighting fast-fashion waste, one sneaker at a time", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:12:34Z"}}, "96": {"text": "The nonprofit SneakCurZ is in the business\u2026 [+2731 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://abcnews.com/Business/wireStory/nonprofit-france-fighting-fast-fashion-waste-sneaker-time-131461818", "title": "A nonprofit in France is fighting fast-fashion waste, one sneaker at a time", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:12:34Z"}}, "97": {"text": "Abercrombie & Fitch ex-CEO is fit for sex trafficking trial\u2014 and he's funny, too, prison doctor tells judge. A prison doctor testified on the third day of Michael Jeffries's competency hearing. The ex-Abercrombie CEO is seeking to be deemed unfit for trial. Michael Jeffries at an event in NYC in 2005The International Center of Photography", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.businessinsider.com/prison-doctor-testifies-ex-abercrombie-ceo-mike-jeffries-mentally-fit-2026-3", "title": "Abercrombie & Fitch ex-CEO is fit for sex trafficking trial\u2014 and he's funny, too, prison doctor tells judge", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:11:01Z"}}, "98": {"text": "<ul><li>Lawyers for the ex-CEO of Abercrombie & Fitch say he's unfit to stand trial for sex trafficking.</li><li>At\u2026 [+3962 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.businessinsider.com/prison-doctor-testifies-ex-abercrombie-ceo-mike-jeffries-mentally-fit-2026-3", "title": "Abercrombie & Fitch ex-CEO is fit for sex trafficking trial\u2014 and he's funny, too, prison doctor tells judge", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:11:01Z"}}, "99": {"text": "Hold on to Your Hardware. A warning about rising prices, vanishing consumer choice, and a future where\nowning a computer may matter more than ever as hardware, power, and control\ndrift toward data centers and away from people. A warning about rising prices, vanishing consumer choice, and a future where\r\nowning a computer may matter more than ever as hardware, power, and control", "metadata": {"source": "https://xn--gckvb8fzb.com/hold-on-to-your-hardware/", "title": "Hold on to Your Hardware", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:10:41Z"}}, "100": {"text": "drift toward data centers and away from peop\u2026 [+25121 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://xn--gckvb8fzb.com/hold-on-to-your-hardware/", "title": "Hold on to Your Hardware", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:10:41Z"}}, "101": {"text": "Japan commits \u20b916,420 crore ODA loan to India for metro, healthcare, agriculture projects. The Government of Japan has committed Official Development Assistance (ODA) loan of JPY 275.858 billion (approx \u20b916,420 Crores) to India for four projects in the sectors of Urban Transport, Health and Agriculture which is to be implemented in the states of Pu\u2026 The Government of Japan has committed Official", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/japan-commits-16420-crore-oda-loan-to-india-for-metro-healthcare-agriculture-projects/article70791871.ece", "title": "Japan commits \u20b916,420 crore ODA loan to India for metro, healthcare, agriculture projects", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:10:24Z"}}, "102": {"text": "The Government of Japan has committed Official Development Assistance (ODA) loan of JPY 275.858 billion (approx 16,420 Crores) to India for four projects in the sectors of Urban Transport, Health and\u2026 [+2533 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/japan-commits-16420-crore-oda-loan-to-india-for-metro-healthcare-agriculture-projects/article70791871.ece", "title": "Japan commits \u20b916,420 crore ODA loan to India for metro, healthcare, agriculture projects", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:10:24Z"}}, "103": {"text": "Amazon\u2019s big bet in AI has been 20 years in the making | CNN Business. Matt Garman helps make your online life \u2013 your Starbucks order, your Netflix binge, your Pinterest browsing\u2013 possible. Matt Garman helps make your online life your Starbucks order, your Netflix binge, your Pinterest browsing possible.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.cnn.com/2026/03/27/tech/amazon-ai-aws-vis", "title": "Amazon\u2019s big bet in AI has been 20 years in the making | CNN Business", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:52Z"}}, "104": {"text": "As the CEO of Amazons cloud computing division, he plays a major role in deciding \u2026 [+7660 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.cnn.com/2026/03/27/tech/amazon-ai-aws-vis", "title": "Amazon\u2019s big bet in AI has been 20 years in the making | CNN Business", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:52Z"}}, "105": {"text": "Chubb\u2019s CEO 25-page shareholder letter touches on China, AI, and the fragility of democracy: \u2018I am both optimistic and I\u2019m concerned\u2019. Also: All the news and watercooler chat from Fortune. Good morning. This is peak season for shareholder letters, in which CEOs share observations about their results, priorities and views of the trends shaping business. Most are short, bland and to the \u2026 [+5403", "metadata": {"source": "https://fortune.com/2026/03/27/chubbs-ceo-evan-greenberg-shareholder-letter-2026-china-ai/", "title": "Chubb\u2019s CEO 25-page shareholder letter touches on China, AI, and the fragility of democracy: \u2018I am both optimistic and I\u2019m concerned\u2019", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:41Z"}}, "106": {"text": "Most are short, bland and to the \u2026 [+5403 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://fortune.com/2026/03/27/chubbs-ceo-evan-greenberg-shareholder-letter-2026-china-ai/", "title": "Chubb\u2019s CEO 25-page shareholder letter touches on China, AI, and the fragility of democracy: \u2018I am both optimistic and I\u2019m concerned\u2019", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:41Z"}}, "107": {"text": "Physical AI: The Next Great Manufacturing Shift. Physical AI, visual tools and wireless automation are converging to transform factory performance and workforce appeal. Manufacturing is at an inflection point. The industry's workforce is ageing, and it has not yet cracked the code on attracting the next generation of workers.\r\nAt the same time, AI tools present a ho\u2026 [+5817 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.techradar.com/pro/physical-ai-the-next-great-manufacturing-shift", "title": "Physical AI: The Next Great Manufacturing Shift", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:31Z"}}, "108": {"text": "Unipart announces strong 2025 financial results. Highlights: Group Turnover reached \u00a3991.6m Underlying PBIT of \u00a327.9m Strengthened balance sheet \u2013 ended year with positive net cash of \u00a39.4m, and our net assets increased by 22.0% to \u00a3145.6m Ranked top logistics provider in the Chartered Institute of Logistic\u2026 Highlights:\r\nTHIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/globe-newswire/unipart-announces-strong-2025-financial-results", "title": "Unipart announces strong 2025 financial results", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:15Z"}}, "109": {"text": "THIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY\r\nSubscribe now to read the latest news in your city and across Canada.\r\n<ul><li>Exclusive articles from Barbara Shecter, Joe O'Connor, Gabri\u2026 [+6059 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/globe-newswire/unipart-announces-strong-2025-financial-results", "title": "Unipart announces strong 2025 financial results", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:15Z"}}, "110": {"text": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister. Balendra Shah was sworn in a day after he released his first public statement since winning the Mar 5 elections, via a rap song posted on social media. KATHMANDU: Nepal's rapper-turned-politician Balendra Shah was sworn in as prime minister on Friday (Mar 27) after sweeping the first election since deadly anti-corruption protests toppled the governm\u2026", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.channelnewsasia.com/asia/nepal-rapper-balendra-shah-sworn-in-prime-minister-6021191", "title": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:00Z"}}, "111": {"text": "anti-corruption protests toppled the governm\u2026 [+2339 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.channelnewsasia.com/asia/nepal-rapper-balendra-shah-sworn-in-prime-minister-6021191", "title": "Nepali rapper Shah sworn in as prime minister", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:09:00Z"}}, "112": {"text": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show. Russia\u2019s crucial Baltic oil ports of Primorsk and Ust-Luga are on fire again after overnight drone attacks, according to data from NASA. (Bloomberg) Russias crucial Baltic oil ports of Primorsk and Ust-Luga are on fire again after overnight drone attacks, according to data from NASA.\r\nTHIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/russias-key-baltic-oil-ports-on-fire-again-satellite-data-show", "title": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:07:06Z"}}, "113": {"text": "THIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONLY\r\nSub\u2026 [+4120 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/russias-key-baltic-oil-ports-on-fire-again-satellite-data-show", "title": "Russia\u2019s Key Baltic Oil Ports on Fire Again, Satellite Data Show", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:07:06Z"}}, "114": {"text": "Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai. Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai ~Sky City Mall, Borivali welcomes the brands second store in India~\r\nMUMBAI, India,\u00a0March 26, 2026\u00a0/PRNewswire/ -- OVS, Italys leading fashion retailer, has officially opened its first store in Mumba\u2026 [+4312 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/brandhub/pr-release/italian-fashion-leader-ovs-opens-its-first-store-in-mumbai/article70791895.ece", "title": "Italian Fashion Leader OVS Opens Its First Store in Mumbai", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:25Z"}}, "115": {"text": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size. Cityflo is expanding its bus services to Kolkata and boosting its fleet in Delhi-NCR. The company now operates over 1,000 buses, three times its size last year. This move makes Cityflo a leading app-based bus operator in India. It aims to provide reliable, pr\u2026 Mumbai: Cityflo said it has scaled its operations in Delhi-NCR and entered Kolkata,", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/roadways/cityflo-enters-new-cities-triples-its-fleet-size/articleshow/129844248.cms", "title": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:03Z"}}, "116": {"text": "its operations in Delhi-NCR and entered Kolkata, taking its total fleet to more than 1,000 buses, three times last years size. The move positions the company among \u2026 [+1775 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/roadways/cityflo-enters-new-cities-triples-its-fleet-size/articleshow/129844248.cms", "title": "Cityflo enters new cities, triples its fleet size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:06:03Z"}}, "117": {"text": "Cregis Nexus Is Now Available on Huawei Cloud Marketplace KooGallery. HONG KONG, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Cregis\r\n, a leading provider of digital asset infrastructure, recently announced the official launch of Cregis Nexus on Huawei Cloud KooGallery\r\n. The on-premise institutional custody infrastructure is now availab\u2026 HONG KONG, March 27, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Cregis", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263649/0/en/Cregis-Nexus-Is-Now-Available-on-Huawei-Cloud-Marketplace-KooGallery.html", "title": "Cregis Nexus Is Now Available on Huawei Cloud Marketplace KooGallery", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:26:00Z"}}, "118": {"text": ", a leading provider of digital asset infrastructure, recently announced the official launch of Cregis Nexus on Huawei Cloud KooGallery\r\n. The on\u2026 [+5739 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263649/0/en/Cregis-Nexus-Is-Now-Available-on-Huawei-Cloud-Marketplace-KooGallery.html", "title": "Cregis Nexus Is Now Available on Huawei Cloud Marketplace KooGallery", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:26:00Z"}}, "119": {"text": "French distributor body SEDPA allies with producers in reply to TV-streamer partnerships. SERIES MANIA: France's distribution trade body Syndicat des Entreprises de Distribution de Programmes Audiovisuels (SEDPA) has forged an alliance with two of the country's producer unions. SEDPA has jo... SERIES MANIA: Frances distribution trade body Syndicat des Entreprises de Distribution de Programmes", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.c21media.net/news/french-distributor-body-sedpa-allies-with-producers-in-reply-to-tv-streamer-partnerships/", "title": "French distributor body SEDPA allies with producers in reply to TV-streamer partnerships", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:25:52Z"}}, "120": {"text": "des Entreprises de Distribution de Programmes Audiovisuels (SEDPA) has forged an alliance with two of the countrys producer unions.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.c21media.net/news/french-distributor-body-sedpa-allies-with-producers-in-reply-to-tv-streamer-partnerships/", "title": "French distributor body SEDPA allies with producers in reply to TV-streamer partnerships", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:25:52Z"}}, "121": {"text": "Iris Bucher\u2026 [+2923 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.c21media.net/news/french-distributor-body-sedpa-allies-with-producers-in-reply-to-tv-streamer-partnerships/", "title": "French distributor body SEDPA allies with producers in reply to TV-streamer partnerships", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:25:52Z"}}, "122": {"text": "Retired Gen. Wesley Clark tangled up in a crypto fraud suit with Burning Man buddies. Sources accuse Clark of \u201cputting his gravitas behind a fraudulent deal\" as a favor to his alternative pal. Sometimes, what goes on the Playa should stay on the Playa.", "metadata": {"source": "https://pagesix.com/2026/03/27/society/retired-gen-wesley-clark-tangled-in-a-crypto-fraud-suit-of-burning-man-buddy/", "title": "Retired Gen. Wesley Clark tangled up in a crypto fraud suit with Burning Man buddies", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:23:30Z"}}, "123": {"text": "A company whose board is chaired by one of America\u2019s most decorated military men has been caught up in a $5 million crypto fraud lawsuit o\u2026 [+2247 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://pagesix.com/2026/03/27/society/retired-gen-wesley-clark-tangled-in-a-crypto-fraud-suit-of-burning-man-buddy/", "title": "Retired Gen. Wesley Clark tangled up in a crypto fraud suit with Burning Man buddies", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:23:30Z"}}, "124": {"text": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Has These Magic: The Gathering Lorwyn Eclipsed Commander Decks at Just $30 Each. Save on a pair of Magic: The Gathering precons for you and a friend to play with right out of the box. Magic: The Gathering\r\n is in the middle of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles set, but the first release on its 2026 roadmap", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.ign.com/articles/amazon-spring-sale-magic-the-gathering-lorwyn-eclipsed-commander-decks-deal", "title": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Has These Magic: The Gathering Lorwyn Eclipsed Commander Decks at Just $30 Each", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:22:24Z"}}, "125": {"text": ", Lorwyn Eclipsed, is still worth picking up - particularly the Commander D\u2026 [+1485 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.ign.com/articles/amazon-spring-sale-magic-the-gathering-lorwyn-eclipsed-commander-decks-deal", "title": "Amazon\u2019s Spring Sale Has These Magic: The Gathering Lorwyn Eclipsed Commander Decks at Just $30 Each", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:22:24Z"}}, "126": {"text": "Europe\u2019s Gas Dilemma Gets More Acute as Storage Season Starts. After a torrid month in which European gas prices surged, plunged and surged again on the war in the Middle East, traders now face a dilemma. (Bloomberg) After a torrid month in which European gas prices surged, plunged and surged again on the war in the Middle East, traders now face a dilemma.", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/europes-gas-dilemma-gets-more-acute-as-storage-season-starts", "title": "Europe\u2019s Gas Dilemma Gets More Acute as Storage Season Starts", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:21:49Z"}}, "127": {"text": "THIS CONTENT IS RESERVED FOR SUBSCRIBERS ONL\u2026 [+4968 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/europes-gas-dilemma-gets-more-acute-as-storage-season-starts", "title": "Europe\u2019s Gas Dilemma Gets More Acute as Storage Season Starts", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:21:49Z"}}, "128": {"text": "Samsung Launches Galaxy Book6 in India with Cutting-Edge Performance and AI-Driven Productivity. Samsung\u2019s Galaxy Book6 series features Intel\u2019s Core Ultra Series 3 processors, extended battery life, and an ultra-slim design that redefines modern PCs  Price starts at INR 127990, with up to 24-month zero-interest EMI Samsung, Indias largest consumer electronics brand, today launched the Galaxy Book6", "metadata": {"source": "https://news.samsung.com/in/samsung-launches-galaxy-book6-in-india-with-cutting-edge-performance-and-ai-driven-productivity", "title": "Samsung Launches Galaxy Book6 in India with Cutting-Edge Performance and AI-Driven Productivity", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:21:11Z"}}, "129": {"text": "brand, today launched the Galaxy Book6 series at a starting price of INR 127990. Samsungs most advanced Galaxy Book series elevates AI-powered productivit\u2026 [+14944 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://news.samsung.com/in/samsung-launches-galaxy-book6-in-india-with-cutting-edge-performance-and-ai-driven-productivity", "title": "Samsung Launches Galaxy Book6 in India with Cutting-Edge Performance and AI-Driven Productivity", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:21:11Z"}}, "130": {"text": "Samsung Display debuts 'QuantumBlack' coating for QD-OLED monitors \u2014 screen tech boosts ambient black levels while reducing glare. If you've been putting off buying a QD-OLED monitor because of your room's lighting setup, Samsung Display might have solved your dilemma. The company's new \"QuantumBlack\" coating finally cuts down on black level raise, reducing purple tint and improving cont\u2026 QD-OLED", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.tomshardware.com/monitors/samsung-display-debuts-quantumblack-coating-for-qd-oled-monitors-screen-tech-boosts-ambient-black-levels-while-reducing-glare", "title": "Samsung Display debuts 'QuantumBlack' coating for QD-OLED monitors \u2014 screen tech boosts ambient black levels while reducing glare", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:20:00Z"}}, "131": {"text": "reducing purple tint and improving cont\u2026 QD-OLED displays have been some of the best monitors you can buy for a few years due to their incredible color volume, but the tech has struggled with rising black levels since its debut. Anytime a l\u2026 [+2575 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.tomshardware.com/monitors/samsung-display-debuts-quantumblack-coating-for-qd-oled-monitors-screen-tech-boosts-ambient-black-levels-while-reducing-glare", "title": "Samsung Display debuts 'QuantumBlack' coating for QD-OLED monitors \u2014 screen tech boosts ambient black levels while reducing glare", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:20:00Z"}}, "132": {"text": "Rebellion return to their AvP roots with Alien Deathstorm, an 80s sci-fi FPS with apocalyptic winds and some slightly naff aliens. Alien Deathstorm is the new sci-fi FPS from Rebellion, developers of skull-popping shooter series Sniper Elite and the recent, Very English survival game Atomfall. What is Alien Deathstorm about? Why, it's a visual novel about a neurodivergent person growing \u2026 Alien", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/rebellion-return-to-their-avp-roots-with-alien-deathstorm-an-80s-sci-fi-fps-with-apocalyptic-winds-and-some-slightly-naff-aliens", "title": "Rebellion return to their AvP roots with Alien Deathstorm, an 80s sci-fi FPS with apocalyptic winds and some slightly naff aliens", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:19:49Z"}}, "133": {"text": "about a neurodivergent person growing \u2026 Alien Deathstorm is the new sci-fi FPS from Rebellion, developers of skull-popping shooter series Sniper Elite and the recent, Very English survival game Atomfall. What is Alien Deathstorm about? Why\u2026 [+1668 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/rebellion-return-to-their-avp-roots-with-alien-deathstorm-an-80s-sci-fi-fps-with-apocalyptic-winds-and-some-slightly-naff-aliens", "title": "Rebellion return to their AvP roots with Alien Deathstorm, an 80s sci-fi FPS with apocalyptic winds and some slightly naff aliens", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:19:49Z"}}, "134": {"text": "aidatapilot added to PyPI. Lightweight Intelligent Data Automation Engine \u2014 plug-and-play pipelines for everyone. \"The first rule of any technology used in a business is that automation applied to an efficient operation will magnify the efficiency.\" Bill Gates\r\nWelcome to aidatapilot. I'm here to guide you from \u2026 [+4876 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://pypi.org/project/aidatapilot/", "title": "aidatapilot added to PyPI", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:19:19Z"}}, "135": {"text": "Dynamic entry of Motor Oil and Alter Ego on ANT1+. Antenna Greece announced an agreement for a subscription-based streaming platform with a Motor Oil Hellas Group company and Alter Ego Media, with the latter two joining its subsidiary ANT1+ as\u2026", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.naftemporiki.gr/english/2091105/dynamic-entry-of-motor-oil-and-alter-ego-on-ant1/", "title": "Dynamic entry of Motor Oil and Alter Ego on ANT1+", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:18:35Z"}}, "136": {"text": "Dynamic entry of Motor Oil and Alter Ego on ANT1+ - \u0397 \u039d\u0391\u03a5\u03a4\u0395\u039c\u03a0\u039f\u03a1\u0399\u039a\u0397 Antenna Greece announced an agreement for a subscription-based streaming platform with a Motor Oil Hellas Group company and Alter Ego Media, with the latter two joining its subsidiary ANT1+ as shareh\u2026 [+785 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.naftemporiki.gr/english/2091105/dynamic-entry-of-motor-oil-and-alter-ego-on-ant1/", "title": "Dynamic entry of Motor Oil and Alter Ego on ANT1+", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:18:35Z"}}, "137": {"text": "Binance Australia hit with multimillion-dollar penalty after retail investor losses. The penalty highlights the critical need for robust compliance and oversight in financial services, especially within the crypto sector.", "metadata": {"source": "https://cryptobriefing.com/binance-australia-penalty-impact/", "title": "Binance Australia hit with multimillion-dollar penalty after retail investor losses", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:18:09Z"}}, "138": {"text": "The post Binance Australia hit with multimillion-dollar penalty after retail investor losses appeared first on Crypto Brie\u2026 ASIC holds Binance accountable for misclassifying clients and highlights the importance of robust crypto compliance. Binance Australia Derivatives, operated by Oztures Trading, has been fined $6.9 mi\u2026 [+2079 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://cryptobriefing.com/binance-australia-penalty-impact/", "title": "Binance Australia hit with multimillion-dollar penalty after retail investor losses", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:18:09Z"}}, "139": {"text": "Harjit Sajjan's startup Juno sees Anduril-type role. A defence technology startup chaired by Harjit Sajjan is raising funds while the country rapidly rearms. Find out more. A defence technology startup chaired by Canadas former defence minister is raising funds while the country rapidly rearms, and launched its first product aimed at Arctic security.\r\nTHIS CONTENT IS RE\u2026 [+4758 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/technology/canada-defense-ministers-startup-juno-anduril", "title": "Harjit Sajjan's startup Juno sees Anduril-type role", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:56Z"}}, "140": {"text": "Canada Ex-Defense Minister\u2019s Startup Juno Sees Anduril-Type Role. A defense technology startup chaired by Canada\u2019s former defense minister is raising funds while the country rapidly rearms, and launched its first product aimed at Arctic security. (Bloomberg) A defense technology startup chaired by Canadas former defense minister is raising funds while the country rapidly rearms, and launched its", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/canada-ex-defense-ministers-startup-juno-sees-anduril-type-role", "title": "Canada Ex-Defense Minister\u2019s Startup Juno Sees Anduril-Type Role", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:56Z"}}, "141": {"text": "the country rapidly rearms, and launched its first product aimed at Arctic security.", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/canada-ex-defense-ministers-startup-juno-sees-anduril-type-role", "title": "Canada Ex-Defense Minister\u2019s Startup Juno Sees Anduril-Type Role", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:56Z"}}, "142": {"text": "THIS C\u2026 [+5422 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://financialpost.com/pmn/business-pmn/canada-ex-defense-ministers-startup-juno-sees-anduril-type-role", "title": "Canada Ex-Defense Minister\u2019s Startup Juno Sees Anduril-Type Role", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:56Z"}}, "143": {"text": "The physical exercises that boost memory and don\u2019t require much effort. Research is increasingly showing that one of the best ways to boost memory, focus and brain health is exercise Your support helps us to tell the story\r\nFrom reproductive rights to climate change to Big Tech, The Independent is on the ground when the story is developing. Whether it's investigating the financia\u2026 [+6609 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.the-independent.com/life-style/health-and-families/exercises-to-improve-memory-yoga-dancing-b2946896.html", "title": "The physical exercises that boost memory and don\u2019t require much effort", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:23Z"}}, "144": {"text": "Checkpoint Partners Rates Lleida.net a Buy at 3.50 Euros per Share. Analyst report identifies a 60-70% discount to sector peers Analyst report identifies a 60-70% discount to sector peers Madrid, March 27, 2026.- Checkpoint Partners has published an analyst report on Lleida.net (BME:LLN) (EPA:ALLLN) with a Buy recommendation and a target price of 3.50 euros per share on a 12-month hor\u2026 [+3429", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263655/0/en/Checkpoint-Partners-Rates-Lleida-net-a-Buy-at-3-50-Euros-per-Share.html", "title": "Checkpoint Partners Rates Lleida.net a Buy at 3.50 Euros per Share", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:00Z"}}, "145": {"text": "of 3.50 euros per share on a 12-month hor\u2026 [+3429 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/27/3263655/0/en/Checkpoint-Partners-Rates-Lleida-net-a-Buy-at-3-50-Euros-per-Share.html", "title": "Checkpoint Partners Rates Lleida.net a Buy at 3.50 Euros per Share", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:00Z"}}, "146": {"text": "Coinbase standoff over stablecoin reward CLARITY is now holding up rules for the entire US crypto market. The stablecoin yield fight has once again consumed the CLARITY Act debate on Capitol Hill, and the cost of that consumption is now measurable. The bill stalled in January when Coinbase objected to its terms, a White House meeting in February failed to break t\u2026 The stablecoin yield fight has", "metadata": {"source": "https://cryptoslate.com/coinbase-standoff-over-stablecoin-reward-clarity-is-now-holding-up-rules-for-the-entire-us-crypto-market/", "title": "Coinbase standoff over stablecoin reward CLARITY is now holding up rules for the entire US crypto market", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:00Z"}}, "147": {"text": "failed to break t\u2026 The stablecoin yield fight has once again consumed the CLARITY Act debate on Capitol Hill, and the cost of that consumption is now measurable.", "metadata": {"source": "https://cryptoslate.com/coinbase-standoff-over-stablecoin-reward-clarity-is-now-holding-up-rules-for-the-entire-us-crypto-market/", "title": "Coinbase standoff over stablecoin reward CLARITY is now holding up rules for the entire US crypto market", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:00Z"}}, "148": {"text": "The bill stalled in January when Coinbase objected to i\u2026 [+10603 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://cryptoslate.com/coinbase-standoff-over-stablecoin-reward-clarity-is-now-holding-up-rules-for-the-entire-us-crypto-market/", "title": "Coinbase standoff over stablecoin reward CLARITY is now holding up rules for the entire US crypto market", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:31:00Z"}}, "149": {"text": "SCOTUS set to deal major blow to mail voting ahead of midterms. Over a dozen states currently accept late mail-in ballots postmarked on election day. That could change In the 2024 election, nearly one in three Americans voted using mail-in or absentee ballots, accounting for some 48 million votes. And despite persistent rhetoric against it, even President Donald Tr\u2026 [+8082 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.salon.com/2026/03/27/scotus-set-to-deal-major-blow-to-mail-voting-ahead-of-midterms/", "title": "SCOTUS set to deal major blow to mail voting ahead of midterms", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:59Z"}}, "150": {"text": "This Tiny Country Has Been Consistently Dumping Bitcoin, And You Won\u2019t Believe How Much. Over the last few months, there have been heavy selling that has contributed to push the Bitcoin price downward. A good chunk of this selling had come from major holders as they moved to secure profits on their holdings. However, amid the sell-offs, one inter\u2026 Over the last few months, there have been heavy", "metadata": {"source": "https://bitcoinist.com/tiny-country-dumping-bitcoin/", "title": "This Tiny Country Has Been Consistently Dumping Bitcoin, And You Won\u2019t Believe How Much", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:56Z"}}, "151": {"text": "Over the last few months, there have been heavy selling that has contributed to push the Bitcoin price downward. A good chunk of this selling had come from major holders as they moved to secure profi\u2026 [+2615 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://bitcoinist.com/tiny-country-dumping-bitcoin/", "title": "This Tiny Country Has Been Consistently Dumping Bitcoin, And You Won\u2019t Believe How Much", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:56Z"}}, "152": {"text": "10 Friday AM Reads. My end-of-week morning train WFH reads: \u2022 I Did Not Predict What Is Going on in Privates: They are not low-volatility, low-correlated (to equities) investments. Not marking something doesn\u2019t make it low risk. I\u2019m not going to rehash it here, but please consul\u2026 I Did Not Predict What Is Going on in Privates: They are not low-volatility, low-correlated (to equities) investments.", "metadata": {"source": "https://ritholtz.com/2026/03/10-friday-am-reads-492/", "title": "10 Friday AM Reads", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:47Z"}}, "153": {"text": "low-correlated (to equities) investments. Not marking something doesnt make it low risk. I\u2019m not going to rehash it here, \u2026 [+2256 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://ritholtz.com/2026/03/10-friday-am-reads-492/", "title": "10 Friday AM Reads", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:47Z"}}, "154": {"text": "The Samsung Galaxy Buds 4 Pro bring new tricks and familiar limitations. Samsung has finally launched the Galaxy Buds 4 Pro, but are they a worthy follow-up to the fun but flawed Buds 3 Pro? Samsungs Galaxy S26 series launch was accompanied by two new pairs of true wireless earbuds. The Galaxy Buds 4 and Galaxy Buds 4 Pro pick up where 2024s Galaxy Buds 3 range left off, albeit without t\u2026 [+8998", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.androidauthority.com/samsung-galaxy-buds-4-pro-review-3642769/", "title": "The Samsung Galaxy Buds 4 Pro bring new tricks and familiar limitations", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:39Z"}}, "155": {"text": "Buds 3 range left off, albeit without t\u2026 [+8998 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.androidauthority.com/samsung-galaxy-buds-4-pro-review-3642769/", "title": "The Samsung Galaxy Buds 4 Pro bring new tricks and familiar limitations", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:39Z"}}, "156": {"text": "Apple Finally Kills the \u2018Fake\u2019 Blur: iPhone 18 Pro Max Leaks Reveal Variable Aperture. Apple is set to redefine smartphone photography with the iPhone 18 Pro Max, addressing long-standing criticisms of its camera system. By introducing significant advancements in low-light performance, zoom capabilities, and overall image quality, the company a\u2026 Apple is set to redefine smartphone photography with", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.geeky-gadgets.com/iphone-18-pro-max-camera-details/", "title": "Apple Finally Kills the \u2018Fake\u2019 Blur: iPhone 18 Pro Max Leaks Reveal Variable Aperture", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:21Z"}}, "157": {"text": "is set to redefine smartphone photography with the iPhone 18 Pro Max, addressing long-standing criticisms of its camera system. By introducing significant advancements in low-light performance,\u2026 [+6519 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.geeky-gadgets.com/iphone-18-pro-max-camera-details/", "title": "Apple Finally Kills the \u2018Fake\u2019 Blur: iPhone 18 Pro Max Leaks Reveal Variable Aperture", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:21Z"}}, "158": {"text": "India Cuts Fuel Taxes and Curbs Exports as Oil Crisis Deepens. India on Friday moved to protect its fuel supply and consumers by reducing domestic taxes on gasoline and diesel and imposing a levy on fuel exports. In view of the West Asia crisis, the central excise duty on petrol and diesel for domestic consumption has be\u2026 Securing Irans enriched uranium likely\u2026\r\nIn Euclid, Ohio, a facility\u2026", "metadata": {"source": "https://oilprice.com/Latest-Energy-News/World-News/India-Cuts-Fuel-Taxes-and-Curbs-Exports-as-Oil-Crisis-Deepens.html", "title": "India Cuts Fuel Taxes and Curbs Exports as Oil Crisis Deepens", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "159": {"text": "In Euclid, Ohio, a facility\u2026\r\nBy Tsvetana Paraskova - Mar 27, 2026, 5:30 AM CDTIndia on Friday moved to protect its fuel supply and consumers by reducing dome\u2026 [+1932 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://oilprice.com/Latest-Energy-News/World-News/India-Cuts-Fuel-Taxes-and-Curbs-Exports-as-Oil-Crisis-Deepens.html", "title": "India Cuts Fuel Taxes and Curbs Exports as Oil Crisis Deepens", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "160": {"text": "7 Apple inventions that reinvented Apple. Macworld", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.macworld.com/article/3100281/7-apple-inventions-that-reinvented-apple.html", "title": "7 Apple inventions that reinvented Apple", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "161": {"text": "As Apple turns 50, it\u2019s easy to focus on the biggest hits, such as the Macintosh, iPod, and iPhone. But the company never relied on a single blockbuster. Instead, its history is paved with a series of ambitious products that arrived at just t\u2026 Skip to contentType your search and hit enter", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.macworld.com/article/3100281/7-apple-inventions-that-reinvented-apple.html", "title": "7 Apple inventions that reinvented Apple", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "162": {"text": "When you purchase through links in our articles, we may earn a small commission. This doesn't affect our editorial independence\r\n.\r\nAs Apple turns 50, i\u2026 [+10199 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.macworld.com/article/3100281/7-apple-inventions-that-reinvented-apple.html", "title": "7 Apple inventions that reinvented Apple", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "163": {"text": "I Asked ChatGPT 500 Questions. Here Are the Ads I Saw Most Often. Ads are rolling out across the US on ChatGPT\u2019s free tier. I asked OpenAI's bot 500 questions to see what these ads were like and how they related to my prompts. OpenAI is starting to stuff the free version of ChatGPT with ads. So, I spent this week asking ChatGPT 500 questions on the mobile app to get a sense of how these new ads", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.wired.com/story/i-asked-chatgpt-500-questions-here-are-the-ads-i-saw-most-often/", "title": "I Asked ChatGPT 500 Questions. Here Are the Ads I Saw Most Often", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "164": {"text": "mobile app to get a sense of how these new ads look as they roll out to mor\u2026 [+3562 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.wired.com/story/i-asked-chatgpt-500-questions-here-are-the-ads-i-saw-most-often/", "title": "I Asked ChatGPT 500 Questions. Here Are the Ads I Saw Most Often", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "165": {"text": "For women's hockey fans, the league's first U.S. broadcast is a watershed moment. Women's hockey has seen record growth since the Olympics. Now, fans say the PWHL's first national broadcast in the U.S. brings visibility the sport deserves. Growing up, Kate Hoos was told girls dont play hockey.", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.nbcnews.com/sports/hockey/womens-hockey-fans-leagues-first-us-broadcast-watershed-moment-rcna264790", "title": "For women's hockey fans, the league's first U.S. broadcast is a watershed moment", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "166": {"text": "If you can find a girls team, well let you play, she recalled being told. But there was no girls team at the time and it wouldnt be until a dec\u2026 [+5649 chars]", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.nbcnews.com/sports/hockey/womens-hockey-fans-leagues-first-us-broadcast-watershed-moment-rcna264790", "title": "For women's hockey fans, the league's first U.S. broadcast is a watershed moment", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27T10:30:00Z"}}, "167": {"text": "\u2018Masterpiece\u2019 1988 film to leave Netflix on March 31 \u2013 90% on Rotten Tomatoes. You only have a few days left to watch this film and it's one you won't want to miss. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/films/2187662/masterpiece-1988-film-leave-netflix", "title": "\u2018Masterpiece\u2019 1988 film to leave Netflix on March 31 \u2013 90% on Rotten Tomatoes", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:47:00"}}, "168": {"text": "Canada launches inquiry on frozen and canned vegetable imports. The federal government has launched a trade inquiry on global imports of frozen and canned vegetables. A statement from the Department of Finance says the government sought the inquiry in response to a request from the Canadian Association of Vegetable Growers and Processors. Domestic producer... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.castanet.net/news/Business/605852/Canada-launches-inquiry-on-frozen-and-canned-vegetable-imports", "title": "Canada launches inquiry on frozen and canned vegetable imports", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:47:00"}}, "169": {"text": "Audi Door Lock Defect Trapped Infant In Back Seat, Suit Says. Electronic door-locking systems in dozens of Audi models intermittently fail to lock or unlock, according to a proposed class action in California federal court, in which a driver alleged the defect once left his infant son trapped in the back seat of his car. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.law360.com/articles/2458476/audi-door-lock-defect-trapped-infant-in-back-seat-suit-says", "title": "Audi Door Lock Defect Trapped Infant In Back Seat, Suit Says", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:14"}}, "170": {"text": "Myrtle Beach community, businesses collecting gift cards for TSA agents. Grand Strand businesses and community members are coming together this weekend to support TSA agents at MYR who went more than a month without pay during the federal government shutdown. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.wmbfnews.com/2026/03/27/myrtle-beach-community-businesses-collecting-gift-cards-tsa-agents/", "title": "Myrtle Beach community, businesses collecting gift cards for TSA agents", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:12"}}, "171": {"text": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size. Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://ng.investing.com/news/sec-filings/nuwellis-announces-resignations-of-two-board-members-and-reduces-board-size-93CH-2415286", "title": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:10"}}, "172": {"text": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size. Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://za.investing.com/news/sec-filings/nuwellis-announces-resignations-of-two-board-members-and-reduces-board-size-93CH-4187181", "title": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:10"}}, "173": {"text": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size. Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://ph.investing.com/news/sec-filings/nuwellis-announces-resignations-of-two-board-members-and-reduces-board-size-93CH-2307628", "title": "Nuwellis announces resignations of two board members and reduces board size", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:09"}}, "174": {"text": "3E Accounting Leverages AI Agents to Deliver 5X Productivity in Corporate Services. Singapore - March 27, 2026 - 3E Accounting Pte Ltd [https://www.3ecpa.com.sg/], a leading provider of company incorporation services and corporate solutions in Singapore, announces the advancement of its AI-powered systems and the development of AI Agents to significantly enhance productivity, ONLY AVAILABLE IN", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.openpr.com/news/4444193/3e-accounting-leverages-ai-agents-to-deliver-5x-productivity", "title": "3E Accounting Leverages AI Agents to Deliver 5X Productivity in Corporate Services", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:05"}}, "175": {"text": "enhance productivity, ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.openpr.com/news/4444193/3e-accounting-leverages-ai-agents-to-deliver-5x-productivity", "title": "3E Accounting Leverages AI Agents to Deliver 5X Productivity in Corporate Services", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:46:05"}}, "176": {"text": "LPKF Laser & Electronics SE (LPKFF) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript. LPKF Laser & Electronics SE (LPKFF) Q4 2025 Earnings Call March 26, 2026 6:00 AM EDTCompany ParticipantsBettina Scha\u0308fer - Head of Investor... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4886750-lpkf-laser-and-electronics-se-lpkff-q4-2025-earnings-call-transcript", "title": "LPKF Laser & Electronics SE (LPKFF) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:58"}}, "177": {"text": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones. KINGSTON, Jamaica - President and CEO of Marathon Insurance Brokers Limited Levar Smith, is calling for major policy reforms to strengthen resilience within Jamaica\u2019s Special Economic Zones (SEZs) warning that the country\u2019s insurance gap leaves billions of dollars in disaster losses uncovered. Smith made the", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "178": {"text": "in disaster losses uncovered. Smith made the call while addressing the Special Economic Zone Authority (SEZA) BAC Accelerator Series on Wednesday under the theme \u2018From Recovery to Resilience: Proactive Policies, Incentives, and Best Practices for Sustainable Investment in SEZs\u2019. Drawing on analysis following Hurricane Melissa, Smith noted that the storm caused an estimated US$12.2 billion in", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "179": {"text": "the storm caused an estimated US$12.2 billion in damage, equivalent to 56.7 per cent of Jamaica\u2019s gross domestic product, but only about US$4.16 billion was covered through a mix of sovereign risk instruments and private insurance. He explained that sovereign coverage totalled US$662 million, including payouts from the Caribbean Catastrophe Risk Insurance Facility (CCRIF), a World Bank parametric", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "180": {"text": "Facility (CCRIF), a World Bank parametric catastrophe bond, and contingency funds, while private market insured losses were estimated at US$3.5 billion. Smith pointed out that combined, this represents roughly 34 per cent of total losses, leaving an uncovered protection gap of approximately US$8 billion. \u201cThe 34 per cent coverage figure is more accurate than earlier reports suggested but it still", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "181": {"text": "than earlier reports suggested but it still means that two thirds of all losses fell on the uninsured,\u201d Smith said, noting that the burden was unevenly distributed. He pointed out that hotels were almost fully insured, while most Jamaican homeowners had little to no coverage. Smith highlighted that insurance penetration varies sharply across sectors. He noted that large commercial properties are", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "182": {"text": "He noted that large commercial properties are generally insured but often below true replacement value, while small and medium-sized enterprises have insurance uptake rates estimated between five and 20 per cent. Smith said among homeowners, only about 20 per cent carry insurance, with the majority underinsured. Turning to SEZs, he warned that their risk exposure extends beyond physical damage,", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "183": {"text": "risk exposure extends beyond physical damage, as these zones depend heavily on uninterrupted operations. Smith warned that disruptions to ports, airports and logistics hubs can lead to immediate income loss and trigger wider economic effects, including job losses, reduced consumer spending and contraction in tourism. He referenced a regional case in which a major Caribbean port sustained", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "184": {"text": "case in which a major Caribbean port sustained hurricane-related losses estimated at between US$12 million and US$20 million. He said recovery within 18 months was made possible through strong pre-loss planning, including updated property valuations, sufficient business interruption coverage, and structured claims processes backed by international reinsurers. Against this background, Smith urged", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "185": {"text": "reinsurers. Against this background, Smith urged policymakers to implement a series of reforms aimed at embedding resilience into SEZ operations. These include mandatory minimum insurance standards tied to current property valuations, linking tax incentives to adequate insurance coverage, and the creation of a SEZ catastrophe pool to reduce premium costs. He also called for increased adoption of", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "186": {"text": "costs. He also called for increased adoption of parametric insurance, particularly for small and medium-sized enterprises, mandatory business continuity planning aligned with insurance programmes, and annual professional valuations for higher-value properties, especially in light of construction cost increases of 35 to 45 per cent following the hurricane. Smith argued that strengthening the", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "187": {"text": "hurricane. Smith argued that strengthening the insurance framework within SEZs is critical to maintaining investor confidence and safeguarding economic stability. \u201cInvestors do not just choose tax incentives they choose stability,\u201d he said, adding that a well-governed insurance system could become one of the country\u2019s strongest competitive advantages. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.jamaicaobserver.com/2026/03/27/marathon-insurance-ceo-calls-mandatory-insurance-standards-special-economic-zones/", "title": "Marathon Insurance CEO calls for mandatory insurance standards in Special Economic Zones", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 22:45:44"}}, "188": {"text": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido. Trust is one of the major legal tenders of marriage. Take away trust from marriage and what is left is carcass. Hypocrisy is another major drawback in marriage. Both can cripple a marriage like a pack of cards. I am a reality TV person. Recently, I have been watching one programme on Facebook, The Honour. Some of [...] The post Mortal", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.vanguardngr.com/2026/03/mortal-betrayal-and-hypocrisy-in-marriage-by-francis-ewherido/", "title": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:36"}}, "189": {"text": "The Honour. Some of [...] The post Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido appeared first on Vanguard News . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.vanguardngr.com/2026/03/mortal-betrayal-and-hypocrisy-in-marriage-by-francis-ewherido/", "title": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:36"}}, "190": {"text": "Fund With Anthropic Stake Extends Drop in Stunning IPO Reversal. Shares of the Fundrise Innovation Fund fell sharply for a second straight day Friday, though remain well above the underlying value of its holdings in private tech firms including the potentially IPO-bound SpaceX and Anthropic PBC. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.livemint.com/market/fund-with-anthropic-stake-extends-drop-in-stunning-ipo-reversal-11774652844279.html", "title": "Fund With Anthropic Stake Extends Drop in Stunning IPO Reversal", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:23"}}, "191": {"text": "Himachal LoP demands CM apologise over misleading Himcare scam figures. The News Mill ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://thenewsmill.com/2026/03/himachal-lop-demands-cm-apologise-over-misleading-himcare-scam-figures/", "title": "Himachal LoP demands CM apologise over misleading Himcare scam figures", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:16"}}, "192": {"text": "Mar 25, 2026; Detroit, Michigan, USA; Atlanta Hawks guard CJ McCollum (3) dribbles in the second half against the Detroit Pistons at Little Caesars Arena. Mandatory Credit: Rick Osentoski-Imagn Images. The Hawks and the Celtics are getting ready to tip things off in Atlanta and this is arguably the top game in the NBA tonight. Atlanta has won 14 of its last 15 ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.si.com/nba/hawks/onsi/news/starting-lineups-revealed-for-atlanta-hawks-vs-boston-celtics-matchup-01kmrjezs8vk", "title": "Mar 25, 2026; Detroit, Michigan, USA; Atlanta Hawks guard CJ McCollum (3) dribbles in the second half against the Detroit Pistons at Little Caesars Arena. Mandatory Credit: Rick Osentoski-Imagn Images", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:00"}}, "193": {"text": "The problem isn\u2019t screens \u2014 it\u2019s why school feels so fake. A UCLA psychology study found adolescents report feeling more authentic on social media than in person \u2014 a finding that complicates school phone bans and forces a harder question about why offline environments feel so performative for young people. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://siliconcanals.com/sc-a-the-problem-isnt-screens-its-why-school-feels-so-fake/", "title": "The problem isn\u2019t screens \u2014 it\u2019s why school feels so fake", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:44"}}, "194": {"text": "The art of karts as season goes pedal to the metal. THE Mildura Kart Club launched into 2026 in fine fashion on Sunday with the beginning of its Club Championship that saw a high-quality day of intense racing action that delivered tight contests, standout performances and no shortage of the track drama spectacle that typically entices motorsport fans across the globe. A star-studded line-up of", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/sport/2026/03/28/the-art-of-karts-as-season-goes-pedal-to-the-metal/", "title": "The art of karts as season goes pedal to the metal", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:22"}}, "195": {"text": "fans across the globe. A star-studded line-up of local [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/sport/2026/03/28/the-art-of-karts-as-season-goes-pedal-to-the-metal/", "title": "The art of karts as season goes pedal to the metal", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:22"}}, "196": {"text": "Q&A | Oliver Luck for Dillon Town Council. Question 1: Voters used a referendum to overturn a planned unit development that granted variances regarding a major project in Dillon\u2019s town core. Voters cited a lack of public benefits given the variances to town code... ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.summitdaily.com/news/qa-oliver-luck-for-dillon-town-council/", "title": "Q&A | Oliver Luck for Dillon Town Council", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:21"}}, "197": {"text": "New steps in Ouyen plan. OUYEN is set to get a new walking and cycling blueprint aimed at improving the township\u2019s road safety for pedestrians and cyclists. Known as the Ouyen Walking and Cycling Plan, the document has been created with funding received last year from the Transport Accident Commission that included a $30,000 Analysis Grant looking into road safety [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/news/2026/03/28/new-steps-in-ouyen-plan/", "title": "New steps in Ouyen plan", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:20"}}, "198": {"text": "into road safety [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/news/2026/03/28/new-steps-in-ouyen-plan/", "title": "New steps in Ouyen plan", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:20"}}, "199": {"text": "Tunisia Boosts Social Safety With World Bank Aid. Washington, March 27, 2026 - The World Bank and the Government of Tunisia are deepening their partnership to strengthen the country's social ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.miragenews.com/tunisia-boosts-social-safety-with-world-bank-aid-1646242/", "title": "Tunisia Boosts Social Safety With World Bank Aid", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:19"}}, "200": {"text": "EU trade deal sealed. AUSTRALIA has struck a long-awaited free trade agreement with the European Union, opening a vast market of 450 million people, but sparking a fierce backlash from farmers who say they have been \u201csold out\u201d. Prime Minister Anthony Albanese announced the deal alongside European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen, calling it a \u201clandmark\u201d agreement that [...] ONLY AVAILABLE", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/news/2026/03/28/eu-trade-deal-sealed/", "title": "EU trade deal sealed", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:18"}}, "201": {"text": "a \u201clandmark\u201d agreement that [...] ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://sunraysiadaily.com.au/news/2026/03/28/eu-trade-deal-sealed/", "title": "EU trade deal sealed", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:06:18"}}, "202": {"text": "Jewler breaks through barriers with Assistive Tech. For a local entrepreneur, jewelry making isn\u2019t just a hobby, it\u2019s her life\u2019s work. Every bead and every wire represents a piece of passion and dedication for Kristi Dilger. But for a time, each bead started getting harder to handle. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.kfyrtv.com/2026/03/27/jewler-breaks-through-barriers-with-assistive-tech/", "title": "Jewler breaks through barriers with Assistive Tech", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:09:01"}}, "203": {"text": "London Business School students study India\u2019s climate finance landscape. Pune: As many as 81 students representing 27 countries and pursuing post-graduate degrees in finance at London Business School visited Mumbai and Pune. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/london-business-school-students-study-indias-climate-finance-landscape/articleshow/129853900.cms", "title": "London Business School students study India\u2019s climate finance landscape", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:09:00"}}, "204": {"text": "Big-Rig Retailer Rolls Into Somers With $3.3 Million I-94 Land Grab. Truck Country has advanced plans for a nearly 49\u2010acre Freightliner dealership west of I\u201094 in Somers after a reported $3.3M land deal; rezoning is required. ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://hoodline.com/2026/03/big-rig-retailer-rolls-into-somers-with-3-3-million-i-94-land-grab/", "title": "Big-Rig Retailer Rolls Into Somers With $3.3 Million I-94 Land Grab", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:08:47"}}, "205": {"text": "Zions Bank CEO to join Utah World Trade Center board. Banking veteran Nate Callister joins the board of directors to strengthen Utah\u2019s global trade and financial infrastructure ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.deseret.com/business/2026/03/27/world-trade-center-utah-names-nate-callister-to-board-of-directors/", "title": "Zions Bank CEO to join Utah World Trade Center board", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:08:24"}}, "206": {"text": "The Long Game: Bill Swartout\u2019s 50-Year Journey from Homework Machines to Lasting Conversations. The ICT pioneer who built systems that made Holocaust survivors immortal and brought museum exhibits to life is stepping back\u2014but not stepping away. The post The Long Game: Bill Swartout\u2019s 50-Year Journey from Homework Machines to Lasting Conversations appeared first on USC Viterbi | School of", "metadata": {"source": "https://viterbischool.usc.edu/news/2026/03/the-long-game-bill-swartouts-50-year-journey-from-homework-machines-to-lasting-conversations/", "title": "The Long Game: Bill Swartout\u2019s 50-Year Journey from Homework Machines to Lasting Conversations", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:08:01"}}, "207": {"text": "appeared first on USC Viterbi | School of Engineering . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://viterbischool.usc.edu/news/2026/03/the-long-game-bill-swartouts-50-year-journey-from-homework-machines-to-lasting-conversations/", "title": "The Long Game: Bill Swartout\u2019s 50-Year Journey from Homework Machines to Lasting Conversations", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:08:01"}}, "208": {"text": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido. Trust is one of the major legal tenders of marriage. Take away trust from marriage and what is left is carcass. Hypocrisy is another major drawback in marriage. Both can cripple a marriage like a pack of cards. I am a reality TV person. Recently, I have been watching one programme on Facebook, The Honour. Some of [...] The post Mortal", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.vanguardngr.com/2026/03/mortal-betrayal-and-hypocrisy-in-marriage-by-francis-ewherido/", "title": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:36"}}, "209": {"text": "The Honour. Some of [...] The post Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido appeared first on Vanguard News . ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "metadata": {"source": "https://www.vanguardngr.com/2026/03/mortal-betrayal-and-hypocrisy-in-marriage-by-francis-ewherido/", "title": "Mortal betrayal and hypocrisy in marriage, by Francis Ewherido", "publishedAt": "2026-03-27 23:07:36"}}, "210": {"text": "Fund With Anthropic Stake Extends Drop in Stunning IPO Reversal. Shares of the Fundrise Innovation Fund fell sharply for a second straight day Friday, though remain well above the underlying value of its holdings in private tech firms including the potentially IPO-bound SpaceX and Anthropic PBC. ONLY AVAILABLE IN P